&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>Language is that which we speak. &lt;br>
Script is that which we use to write words of any language.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Hindi is a language not a script. English is a language not a script.&lt;br>
Tamil is a language and script.&lt;br>
Devanaagari is script to write mainly Hindi, Napali, Marathi languages.&lt;br>
Roman is script to write European languages like English or Spanish.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>